# iCloud account for colinstein@me.com
IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
AuthMechs LOGIN
User colinstein
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -c 'mutt' -D 'email password' -a 'colinstein@me.com' -w"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem
IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud
MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/.mail/icloud/
Inbox ~/.mail/icloud/Inbox
Channel icloud
Master :icloud-remote:
Slave :icloud-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
